Assistant QA Manager (Electronics Account)
Responsibilities
Key Responsibilities:The key objective is to ensure QA Department is running smoothly and to maintain the implementation of ISO 9001:2008 as expected.Reporting to: QA & EHS Manager Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor Degree (S1) in any discipline. Degree in Engineering background would be an advantage.At least 4 years of working experience in Quality Assurance or Quality Control in Manufacturing or Logistics IndustryFamiliar with ISO 9001:2008 MR implementation or Internal Audit Certification is a must.Able to work under pressure and tight scheduleHonest, determine, energetic, pro-active and self-motivatedGood command of English both oral and writtenComputer literate (MS Word, Excel and Power point)Office location : Cibitung Interested applicants are invited to email your comprehensive resume inclusive of expected salary and recent photograph to:                                                                            recruitment.indo@ych.com                                     Please put the Job Title of the position in the subject line of your email                                                                                    PT. YCH Indonesia                                                      Jl. Kalimalang KM.2 Cibitung - Bekasi - West Java                                                                               Website: www.ych.com
